section.section:
"Firearm" includes:
a handgun, antique firearm, rifle, shotgun, short-barreled shotgun, or short-barreled rifle as those terms are defined in § 4-201 of this title;
an assault pistol as defined in § 4-301 of this title;
a machine gun as defined in § 4-401 of this title; and
a regulated firearm as defined in § 5-101 of the Public Safety Article.
